  "texts": [
    "We evaluated two PEFT methods on a server equipped with two RTX 3090Ti (24G) GPUs and assessed their impact on the performance of CPMI-ChatGLM.",
    "We used the Rouge_chinese 23 and NLTK 24 toolkits to calculate ROUGE and BLEU scores respectively, and BARTScore calculation was performed using the default parameter configuration.",
    "Figure 1 shows the training loss curves of the two PEFT methods, and the models converged at around 3000 steps.",
    "The smooth loss curves indicate stable performance improvement and effective training.",
    "Furthermore, as shown in Fig. 2, CPMI-ChatGLM fine-tuned using the P-Tuning v2 method outperformed LoRA in all aspects."
  ],
